0Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 唔明點解開大門出去唔掩好/唔關好, 由得隻貓自己走出去<br />\n2. 會唔會跳窗, 係咪所有窗都裝好貓網?<br />\n3. 會唔會根本仲係屋企入面只係&quot;呢埋&quot;咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係門未關好出左去 屋企有裝窗網"},{"pid":"96cc804e6ca75575583fe3123a9dae2792d57a10","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇掛鎯鎯</blockquote><br />\n冇掛野係頸到 佢唔鍾意"},{"pid":"e8f7e71dbeb4a7302ddcd32a3c0c3a277cdd6bbe","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:12:50.000Z","msg":"屋企另一貓成日想搵佢玩 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62ac2f330fd2af23ef2400bdfcfb5445bfb0e21","tid":228433,"uid":58125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"0da788f6080473e5d1b60de16a82bd7ffeea8a4e","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 唔明點解開大門出去唔掩好/唔關好, 由得隻貓自己走出去<br />\n2. 會唔會跳窗, 係咪所有窗都裝好貓網?<br />\n3. 會唔會根本仲係屋企入面只係&quot;呢埋&quot;咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係門未關好出左去 屋企有裝窗網</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋有時真係睇唔到佢出左去 試過返屋企關左門 我媽先同我講你見唔到佢衝左出去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fde11839031053204dfcecf99d6a87f559a06b6","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>村民幫推<br />\n已叫屋企人留意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24728e992dd2d3e6036dfd2dbc1def9083886ed7","tid":228433,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91798647ad3ca7c9da622c0955c27af328b6dace","tid":228433,"uid":8471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"好有可能同一層啲人見有隻貓 好心收養左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bdc81576992d2da10bfb1388d795e04dd97208","tid":228433,"uid":2795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"逐家逐戶拍門啦"},{"pid":"c9281660900b42a0dcda6ba16eebad1d47938c9a","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有可能同一層啲人見有隻貓 好心收養左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同層既都識都有問過 同埋有兩三戶都有養寵物"},{"pid":"70277647d10dad730e001d2871b7aadb6bead2d1","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逐家逐戶拍門啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果其他層數發現有貓應該都會通知管理處 我地都申請緊係大堂貼幾日尋貓啟事"},{"pid":"f1dcfb4429ce9a0083b50c62d69f809074b57354","tid":228433,"uid":8229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"琴日青雅苑後門見過有隻全黑 <br />\n大概係1045左右 <br />\n唔知係咪樓豬個隻"},{"pid":"8b667f214aae39753c138bee9f23315d6d5c95aa","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴日青雅苑後門見過有隻全黑 <br />\n大概係1045左右 <br />\n唔知係咪樓豬個隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝提供資料 今晚會去搵下"},{"pid":"15b0a2cd483274aa4f4eeda17bc399e5762d1791","tid":228433,"uid":8229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>琴日青雅苑後門見過有隻全黑 <br />\n大概係1045左右 <br />\n唔知係咪樓豬個隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝提供資料 今晚會去搵下</blockquote><br />\n我見佢身型步法唔太像野喵，<br />\n走近佢都唔會狂奔，<br />\n施施然入草"},{"pid":"811772f1ee853ff9c4b73a2d3737b7331b51386c","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ugs41qya\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fugs41qya&h=39332383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩道又重 開完又關得快既防煙門 如果佢要跟人入到後樓梯一定要貼住開門個個人行先有機會入到 所以都諗緊係咪入左LIFT去左其他層係人地屋企 個家屋企又唔到樓下管理處講"},{"pid":"b4d6013bfb9165d017d7d4a31b21cef27205c49e","tid":228433,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58bcbec157f6f24bb11fc3b663786968b180975c","tid":228433,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df95f6230c2e7282db47e550f9bdee4294fc19e5","tid":228433,"uid":2250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f179ffdda84c904b78190dd61a3433fbf218a2","tid":228433,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T19:50:38.000Z","msg":"我有FD試過一次以為唔見貓<br />\n點知係隻貓係個衣櫃到幾日唔出黎<br />\n雖然好似好on9但係你得閒搵下佢會唔會係d櫃入面"},{"pid":"f6b2f80097c3915be0b453516c2d3deed5d2695f","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T20:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有FD試過一次以為唔見貓<br />\n點知係隻貓係個衣櫃到幾日唔出黎<br />\n雖然好似好on9但係你得閒搵下佢會唔會係d櫃入面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全間屋搵晒 櫃桶都拉埋出黎睇入面有冇 佢係屋企比我地困住左佢一定會喵到我地搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a285348351b4e0e85257075a28db85cf448cb7","tid":228433,"uid":92063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T20:11:32.000Z","msg":"去樓上樓下都拍門問下人"},{"pid":"3d934c2cc738a85b32c86102ca1aa29681b1a83c","tid":228433,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T20:11:39.000Z","msg":"樓主又唔擺低聯絡資料<br />\n見到仲要上黎講 講完 再等你睇到<br />\n隻貓都唔知走左去邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dfbb