>會唔會係你d鄰居收埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有可能入左去 鄰居都唔知"},{"pid":"d618c0bd603de9b2bf39692c76bb61866c10fb17","tid":228433,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 唔明點解開大門出去唔掩好/唔關好, 由得隻貓自己走出去<br />\n2. 會唔會跳窗, 係咪所有窗都裝好貓網?<br />\n3. 會唔會根本仲係屋企入面只係&quot;呢埋&quot;咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好正常，因為有防煙門，其他人又唔會開住門，suppose隻貓只會喺走廊行下散下步，有時我隻貓對住大門不斷喵，我都會放會出去行個圈，貓都要有自由架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"34fab34597f6f74acd8871b7ea9565973f487984","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1. 唔明點解開大門出去唔掩好/唔關好, 由得隻貓自己走出去<br />\n2. 會唔會跳窗, 係咪所有窗都裝好貓網?<br />\n3. 會唔會根本仲係屋企入面只係&quot;呢埋&quot;咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好正常，因為有防煙門，其他人又唔會開住門，suppose隻貓只會喺走廊行下散下步，有時我隻貓對住大門不斷喵，我都會放會出去行個圈，貓都要有自由架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係 我兩隻貓會一齊出去行下 行完返到屋企會好開心"},{"pid":"e232bfe397dedf87ca248c8eb401ab13d224be34","tid":228433,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會係你d鄰居收埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有可能入左去 鄰居都唔知</blockquote><br />\n最怕係覺得好可愛 唔拎返出黎"},{"pid":"32caffadc7190648fbaf4c8217d4b0457fc757a8","tid":228433,"uid":24207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"推呀，希望樓主快Ｄ搵返貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dc5a6f6c7fe7cd4a638f10f78952fd23ed26e0","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會係你d鄰居收埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有可能入左去 鄰居都唔知</blockquote><br />\n最怕係覺得好可愛 唔拎返出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢好怕人 我同屋企人都用左成年時間先可以真係摸佢"},{"pid":"7dab5b3fdfb3e88748ff82cc84c48146c8ae04fa","tid":228433,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"問下漁農愛協<br />\n我試過走貓去左人屋企，人地call愛協<br />\n要快，遲左唔知會唔會啪"},{"pid":"a5077136c62a31790577a80d2b6f5e33dd2da43f","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問下漁農愛協<br />\n我試過走貓去左人屋企，人地call愛協<br />\n要快，遲左唔知會唔會啪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係愛協同漁農處都登記左失貓"},{"pid":"80285615716eac64626ac7cf64e176888ee0cf77","tid":228433,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9cogdt4q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9cogdt4q&h=ac8dd155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b9k504ng\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb9k504ng&h=ccd820e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加多兩張相 希望搵得到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab5af45647d21b145ad22c8ba7aa921509159b5","tid":228433,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"防煙門佢開唔到<br />\nlift如果開門姐係有人要上/落<br />\n一定會有人見到<br />\n住幾樓? 會唔會跳左去平台"}]}